# .htaccess für API-Ordner
# CORS Konfiguration für www.haukeschultz.com

<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "https://www.haukeschultz.com"
    Header set Access-Control-Allow-Methods "GET, POST, OPTIONS"
    Header set Access-Control-Allow-Headers "Content-Type"
</IfModule>

# Setze Standard-Datei
DirectoryIndex highscores.php

# Verhindere Directory Listing
Options -Indexes